        <content type="html" xml:base="https://adityaaswani.com/blog/building-this-website/">&lt;h1 id=&quot;building-this-website-a-journey-with-zola-and-modern-web-technologies&quot;&gt;Building This Website: A Journey with Zola and Modern Web Technologies&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#building-this-website-a-journey-with-zola-and-modern-web-technologies&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: building-this-website-a-journey-with-zola-and-modern-web-technologies&quot;&gt;üîó&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When I decided to rebuild my personal website, I wanted something that would be fast, maintainable, and showcase modern web development practices. After evaluating various options, I landed on Zola with the Abridge theme‚Äîa decision that proved to be excellent for performance and developer experience.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;why-i-chose-zola&quot;&gt;Why I Chose Zola&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#why-i-chose-zola&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: why-i-chose-zola&quot;&gt;üîó&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Static site generators have come a long way, and the ecosystem offers many excellent options. Here‚Äôs why Zola stood out for me:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;performance-first&quot;&gt;Performance First&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#performance-first&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: performance-first&quot;&gt;üîó&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zola is built in Rust, which means it‚Äôs incredibly fast. The build times are lightning quick, even for large sites, and the generated output is optimized for performance out of the box.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;simple-yet-powerful&quot;&gt;Simple Yet Powerful&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#simple-yet-powerful&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: simple-yet-powerful&quot;&gt;üîó&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unlike some other static site generators that can become complex quickly, Zola strikes a perfect balance. It‚Äôs powerful enough for sophisticated sites but simple enough that you don‚Äôt need to fight the framework.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;modern-web-standards&quot;&gt;Modern Web Standards&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#modern-web-standards&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: modern-web-standards&quot;&gt;üîó&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zola embraces modern web standards and generates clean, semantic HTML. This was important to me as someone who cares about web accessibility and SEO.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;the-abridge-theme-performance-meets-aesthetics&quot;&gt;The Abridge Theme: Performance Meets Aesthetics&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#the-abridge-theme-performance-meets-aesthetics&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: the-abridge-theme-performance-meets-aesthetics&quot;&gt;üîó&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choosing the right theme was crucial. The Abridge theme caught my attention because of its focus on performance and modern design principles.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;key-features-that-sold-me&quot;&gt;Key Features That Sold Me&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#key-features-that-sold-me&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: key-features-that-sold-me&quot;&gt;üîó&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;‚ö° Lighthouse Perfect Scores&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
The theme consistently achieves perfect Lighthouse scores across all metrics‚Äîperformance, accessibility, best practices, and SEO.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;üé® Clean, Semantic HTML&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
The generated markup is clean and semantic, making it accessible and SEO-friendly without sacrificing design flexibility.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;üîß No Mandatory JavaScript&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
