&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Maintainability&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;: Modular architecture enables rapid feature development&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;future-enhancements&quot;&gt;Future Enhancements&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#future-enhancements&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: future-enhancements&quot;&gt;üîó&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Analytics&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;: Machine learning integration for predictive insights&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mobile App&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;: React Native companion app for mobile analytics&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
